snippet.title: Crack (Amiga) (Gameplay)
snippet.description:
----about:----------------------------------------
Yet unreleased gameplay-Videos from various OLD Games. There are still a few which didn`t make it to YouTube - hard to believe, but true. I just...DIG THEM OUT ! :) Feel free to discuss about the Game in the comments.
---------------------------------------------------

Crack (c)1988 Linel
Intro-Music by: Tony Vera Diaz ( http://www.aural-stimulation.net )

Testberichte und Kommentare zum Spiel: http://www.kultboy.com/testbericht-uebersicht/4847/

My thoughts about the Game: oh,well. Just another Breakout/Arkanoid/Krakout/Whatever-clone. This one comes along with a prehistorically scenario, a stupid Mini-Game and a Ball who differs not enough from the background-Pictures. 80 Not a bad Game at all, but there are better ones available.
